title: 'The Gilmore Girls' is being revived on Netflix
text:
Published By: USATODAY.com: TV - Today 
'The Gilmore Girls' ended on a low note, but thanks to Netflix and creator Amy Sherman-Palladino, the show is getting another chance at a go...
